OL,6,FShe said: "This is such an important
OL,7,Fdebate and it's such an important
OL,8,Fmoment for this movement for the Isle
OL,9,Fof Man, because really, if if the Isle
OL,10,Fof Man can do this, it's very likely
OL,11,Fto spread to the mainland.
OL,13,F"We know that Scotland is doing it,
OL,14,Fand this is a compassionate choice for
OL,15,Fpeople at the end of life", she argued.
OL,17,FRamsey MHK Dr Alex Allinson introduced
OL,18,Fa bill in 2022, which would give
OL,19,Fterminally-ill adults the right to end
OL,20,Ftheir own life, with medical
OL,21,Fassistance.
