OL,6,FAnti-assisted dying campaigner Peter
OL,7,FMurcott has said the assisted dying
OL,8,Fbill has 'many legal flaws', and is
OL,9,F'against the will of God'.
OL,11,FThe former law lecturer describes the
OL,12,Fbill as 'assisted suicide', claiming
OL,13,Fthat there are many on the island who
OL,14,Fare against the proposed change.
