OL,4,CMan
OL,6,FSpeaking outside Tynwald, he said: "On
OL,7,FMay the 17th 2023, government adopted
OL,8,Fa suicide prevention strategy. Now
OL,9,Fthis becomes a suicide provision
OL,10,Fstrategy, because the bill is about
OL,11,Fassisted suicide, about amending the
OL,12,Fexisting law.
OL,14,F"I cannot understand how you can spend
OL,15,Fpublic money on providing something
OL,16,Fthat you're going to prevent because
OL,17,Fthe prevention strategy takes public
OL,18,Fmoney, and this bill will take public
OL,19,Fmoney - trying to do two contradictory
OL,20,Fthings."
